clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"meet_our_content\">\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<div class=\"padt5\">&quot;10EQS\' unique platform allows me to work in a seamless manner with other consultants and experts to create workable and valuable solutions for clients. Experts and Consultants like me benefit from the learning we get from collaborating real time on 10EQS, increasing our cumulative domain knowledge and building long lasting relationships with our peers. 10EQS creates a win-win scenario for all the stakeholders and I am happy to be associated with it.&quot;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div align=\"right\" class=\"padt5\"><a href=\"/teneqs_experts\">Learn more &raquo;</a></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>','Consultant Spotlight',2),(5,'<div class=\"clear padt3\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><a title=\"Latest news from 10EQS\" href=\"/newsfrom_teneqs\">Latest news from 10EQS</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"clear padt10\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><a title=\"BusinessWeek\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/05_25/b3938601.htm\"> <img height=\"16\" border=\"none\" width=\"75\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/businessweek_img.png\" alt=\"\" /> </a></div>\r\n<div><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/magazine/content/05_25/b3938601.htm\">   The Power of us-Mass collaboration on the internet is shaking up businesses   </a></div>\r\n<div class=\"clear padt10\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><a title=\"Wikinomics\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.wikinomics.com/blog/index.php/about/\"><img height=\"47\" border=\"none\" width=\"31\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/wikinomics_img.png\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n<div><a title=\"Wikinomics\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.wikinomics.com/blog/index.php/about/\">Wikinomics: How Mass Collaboration Changes Everything</a></div>\r\n<div class=\"clear padt10\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div><a title=\"The wisdom of crowds\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.randomhouse.com/feature