:\"#required\";b:1;s:14:\"#default_value\";s:15:\"News from 10EQS\";s:10:\"#maxlength\";i:255;s:7:\"#weight\";i:-5;}s:10:\"body_field\";a:7:{s:12:\"#after_build\";a:2:{i:0;s:14:\"node_teaser_js\";i:1;s:26:\"node_teaser_include_verify\";}s:7:\"#prefix\";s:32:\"<div class=\"body-field-wrapper\">\";s:7:\"#suffix\";s:6:\"</div>\";s:9:\"teaser_js\";a:5:{s:5:\"#type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:5:\"#rows\";i:10;s:7:\"#teaser\";s:9:\"edit-body\";s:16:\"#teaser_checkbox\";s:19:\"edit-teaser-include\";s:9:\"#disabled\";b:1;}s:14:\"teaser_include\";a:5:{s:5:\"#type\";s:8:\"checkbox\";s:6:\"#title\";s:25:\"Show summary in full view\";s:14:\"#default_value\";b:1;s:7:\"#prefix\";s:29:\"<div class=\"teaser-checkbox\">\";s:7:\"#suffix\";s:6:\"</div>\";}s:4:\"body\";a:5:{s:5:\"#type\";s:8:\"textarea\";s:6:\"#title\";s:4:\"Body\";s:14:\"#default_value\";s:2436:\"<div id=\"full_news\">\r\n<p>Dear 10EQS community,</p>\r\n<p>At 10EQS we are excited about the future and what it&nbsp;holds for our company. We believe that we are at the forefront of the web 3.0 transformation &ndash; enabling people to collaborate and solve complex business issues in a truly seamless environment. We have now tried out our model on a set of challenging client engagements with encouraging results. The knowledge revolution begins now.</p>\r\n<p>A key reason for why we are confident about our future is because of our experts. The experts which &ldquo;drive&rdquo; the 10EQS knowledge platform are the reason for our progress to date and they will be the reason for our success in the future. We believe 10EQS to be an exceptional company - a company of people proud of the work they do, the solutions they provide and the knowledge revolution they are part of. 10EQS is an organization defined by the character and integrity of its people.</p>\r\n<p>As we work to serve our clients, to build strong relationships and deliver innovative and creative solutions to their business challenges, we rely on our core principles to guide our decisions and actions, ensuring everything we do are beneficial to the client, or experts and our colleagues.</p>\r\n<p>I speak for all of the exceptional experts and employees at 10EQS when I say we are totally committed to providing cheap, distinct, targeted knowledge to our clients. We believe our responsibility is not only to ensure that we continue to live up to the standards we have set, but also to advance our service to our clients to even higher levels.</p>\r\n<p>As 10EQS&rsquo;s business grows, so does our opportunity to have a greater impact on the world around us. Our recent series of meetings in Silicon Valley where we met the globally leading players within crowd solving, professional networking as well as venture capitalists only strengthened our belief in the soundness of our mission and the uniqueness and the inherent potential that it embodies.</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your interest in 10EQS and for visiting our website. I hope you find it informative. However, if you really want to get to know us and what we can do to help you address your business challenges then please contact us. We welcome the opportunity to connect with you and to contribute to your success.</p>\r\n<p>Your sincerely,</p>\r\n<strong>Henrik  Poppe<br />\r\nChief  Executive Officer</strong></div>\";s:5:\"#rows\";i:20;s:9:\"#required\";b:0;}s:6:\"format\";a:10:{s:5:\"#type\";s:8:\"fieldset\";s:6:\"#title\";s:12:\"Input format\";s:12:\"#collapsible\";b:1;s:10:\"#collapsed\";b:1;s:7:\"#weight\";N;s:17:\"#element_validate\";a:1:{i:0;s:20:\"filter_form_validate\";}i:1;a:7:{s:5:\"#type\";s:5:\"radio\";s:6:\"#title\";s:13:\"Filtered HTML\";s:14:\"#default_value\";s:1:\"2\";s:13:\"#return_value\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"#parents\";a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"format\";}s:12:\"#description\";s:306:\"<ul class=\"tips\"><li>Web page addresses and e-mail addresses turn into links automatically.</li><li>Allowed HTML tags: &lt;a&gt; &lt;em&gt; &lt;strong&gt; &lt;cite&gt; &lt;code&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;ol&gt; &lt;