INSERT INTO `node_revisions` VALUES (1,1,1,'Why 10EQS','<p>To meet today&rsquo;s complex and fast-moving business challenges, you need to harness world-class expertise on-demand &ndash; but at a budget you are willing to pay. Use 10EQS Knowledge Exchange, a global platform that finds answers to client questions, enabling you to leverage the global reach of the Internet and the &ldquo;wisdom of crowds&rdquo; to address critical business needs with unsurpassed efficiency, quality, and speed. Unlike other sites, we are not just a phone directory of experts; through 10EQS Knowledge Exchange, experts will solve your business problems.</p>\r\n<p>Once a 10EQS client, obtaining knowledge to solve business issues is easy: you specify your question, and the rest is up to us: we will find the right experts, get them to answer your question, and take care of all contractual, invoicing and payments processes that are required through one seamless automated process.</p>\r\n<h2>Getting access to the  right experts.</h2>\r\n<p>We match your business issues to a carefully chosen group of experts that specialize in the very specific areas that you are concerned with, and we do this with proprietary technology which is at the heart of what makes us different. The 10EQS platform breaks up your complex problems into small, self-contained tasks; qualified professionals anywhere in the world can then quickly and efficiently work on these tasks to provide solutions, which have to meet our rigorous quality standards. Whenever needed, you will even get different points of view from several experts on a question.</p>\r\n<h2>Using advanced  collaboration techniques to solve your problems.</h2>\r\n<p>In 10EQS, experts will work together in a competitive yet collaborative environment, combining the dynamics of competition with the creativity of collaboration. Our unique approach of matching consultants to tasks, ranking performance dynamically, and using rigorous merit-based compensation has only one objective: finding the best solution for your critical business issues.</p>\r\n<h2>Offering efficiency,  quality, speed.</h2>\r\n<p>Our new approach to obtain knowledge achieves unprecedented efficiency, quality and speed. By precisely defining client issues and working with seasoned industry experts ideally suited to each issue, 10EQS eliminates rework, idle time and learning curves, thus achieving efficiency. By reaching out to a global professional community which competes and collaborates to find the best answer for each client problem, 10EQS achieves quality. By breaking up complex engagements into small tasks and using parallel processing, allowing experts from anywhere to contribute at any time, 10EQS achieves speed.</p>','<p>To meet today&rsquo;s complex and fast-moving business challenges, you need to harness world-class expertise on-demand &ndash; but at a budget you are willing to pay. Use 10EQS Knowledge Exchange, a global platform that finds answers to client questions, enabling you to leverage the global reach of the Internet and the &ldquo;wisdom of crowds&rdquo; to address critical business needs with unsurpassed efficiency, quality, and speed. Unlike other sites, we are not just a phone directory of experts; through 10EQS Knowledge Exchange, experts will solve your business problems.</p>','',1265611266,2),(2,2,1,'Our clients','<p>10EQS works with large corporations around the globe. We are ready to service multiple industries and functions, including financial services, consumer goods and telecommunications. We also serve investment banks and private equity firms.  Within each client organization, we work on all levels, including CEO, CFO, head of strategy or business development, controlling, business unit heads, or individual professionals in any business or functional unit. Since we concentrate on specific questions that can be solved in a short period of time, we can work on knowledge engagements with a small budget, allowing many executives in any organization to use the services of our platform directly.</p>','<p>10EQS works with large corporations around the globe. We are ready to service multiple industries and functions, including financial services, consumer goods and telecommunications. We also serve investment banks and private equity firms.  Within each client organization, we work on all levels, including CEO, CFO, head of strategy or business development, controlling, business unit heads, or individual professionals in any business or functional unit.','',1265278017,2),(3,3,1,'Our experts','\r\n                      <p>We believe that you will get  the best answer to your question if we look for anyone that may have the right  expertise to work on your project. That is why we are recruiting for our  quickly growing pool of experts among the whole world of professionals; we are  not confined to just a limited group of employees or anyone single network. And  we select the right expert for your engagement only on the basis of proven  success on our platform. This is why our experts can provide immediate answers  and do not first have to acquire the expertise for your issue.</p>\r\n                          <h2>10EQS experts are a  select group. </h2>\r\n                          <p>When looking for the right people to work on your question,  10EQS will look for those experts that have actually already done similar work  and thus are qualified through actual performance (not through formal  qualifications like a CV that may be difficult to assess). For each individual  task, our system will search literally through thousands of expert profiles,  identifying those that precisely match the requirements of the task at hand.</p>\r\n                          <h2>10EQS experts are  passionate about their work. </h2>\r\n                          <p>Since our experts choose when  and on which issues to work, they control over their professional lives with  the flexibility to pursue their passions. And since compensation depends only  on the solution of tasks, not on the time spent, the motivation to come up with  the right solution is as high as can be.</p>\r\n                      <h2>10EQS experts are mature and experienced. </h2>\r\n                      <p>We are recruiting experts on a continuous basis to  register on our site and work on client projects. Since we are matching each  individual task precisely to the qualifications needed for solving it and  qualifications are different for each task, our pool of experts spans a wide  range: we have experts with multi-year experience for difficult advisory-type  engagements, and we have experts that have an analyst background for  engagements in which fact-finding is the key activity. And since our task  matching algorithm will find the best person for each individual task, we do  not have \"learning curves\"; we use expensive talent only when truly needed.</p>\r\n                     \r\n                      <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n                      <p>We believe that you will get  the best answer to your question if we look for anyone that may have the right  expertise to work on your project. That is why we are recruiting for our  quickly growing pool of experts among the whole world of professionals; we are  not confined to just a limited group of employees or anyone single network. And  we select the right expert for your engagement only on the basis of proven  success on our platform. This is why our experts can provide immediate answers  and do not first have to acquire the expertise for your issue.</p>','',1265278821,2),(4,4,1,'When to work with us','                    \r\n                      <p>At 10EQS, we understand that  there are an infinite number of projects and situations in the business world.  If you are unsure whether 10EQS Knowledge Exchange is the right solution for  you, please read through the following checklist. We recommend to use our  platform:</p>\r\n                      <ul>\r\n                        <li>When you have a specific question that needs to  be answered quickly and efficiently</li>\r\n                        <li>When the answer to your question requires deep  industry expertise that you do not have in-house and where you believe that  even large consulting organizations may not have the expertise that is needed</li>\r\n                        <li>When the knowledge that you need is global in  nature and requires the cooperation of many different people in many different  locations around the world</li>\r\n                        <li>When you want to avoid the hassle of finding all  the people needed, negotiate contracts with them, and take care of compensation  and payment processes</li>\r\n                        <li>When you want to get the best leverage from your  budget rather than spending what is typically needed for a large consulting  firm on a complex, open ended question</li>\r\n                      </ul><div class=\"padt5\"></div>\r\n                      <p>Example of knowledge  engagements that we have carried out recently include a market assessment for a  major telecom provider, best practice marketing analysis for a major European  financial institution, a portfolio analysis for a major international investment  bank, and market assessment for major credit card providers.</p>\r\n                      <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                      <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                      <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                      <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','                    \r\n                      <p>At 10EQS, we understand that  there are an infinite number of projects and situations in the business world.  If you are unsure whether 10EQS Knowledge Exchange is the right solution for  you, please read through the following checklist. We recommend to use our  platform:</p>','',1265278953,2),(5,5,1,'How to work with us','\r\n                      <p>Using 10EQS Knowledge  Exchange is an easy and straightforward process: you tell us which specific  question you would like to have answered and what you are willing to pay for it  and we will do the rest. You don’t have to worry about finding the right people,  contracting and paying them – this is all done by us. Here you find the details  of how it works.</p>\r\n                          <h2>Contacting us and  defining a question.</h2>\r\n                          <p>Contacting 10EQS Knowledge Exchange is easy: just send us an email under <a href=\"mailto:clients@10EQS.com\">clients@10EQS.com</a> and let us know which question we should answer. A 10EQS Knowledge Manager will  contact you with a specific proposal on how to answer your question and what  the suggested budget will be. Once we agree with you on the knowledge requested  and on the budget, we will post your question on our site and have our expert  community work on it.</p>\r\n                      <h2>Questions for which 10EQS  Knowledge Exchange is suitable.</h2>\r\n                          <p>The Knowledge Exchange has set up processes  for two types of questions: fact finding and advice. Fact finding engagements  typically involve numerical data needed as input for strategic decision making;  advisory engagements include interpretations of facts, projections, and  insights into specific markets or company situations. Often client engagements  include both types of questions. We work best when we receive clearly defined  business issues that we can easily transport into the structure of our platform  – something our Knowledge Manager will do for you.</p>\r\n                          <h2>Posting your question on  our site.</h2>\r\n                          <p>When we post your question on our site, we will split it up into  its individual components, each of which forms an individual task that is fully  self-explanatory and that can be worked on independently by our experts. This  process allows massive parallel processing since many experts can work on the  individual question components at the same time. In addition, your  confidentiality will be fully maintained because the individual tasks do not  allow concluding which company has posted the question to which this particular  task belongs.</p>\r\n                        <p>Finding right experts and  working out all of the required agreements is a fully automated process. Once  your questions – actually all of the tasks that form it – have been posted on  our site, our system will identify automatically those experts that have the  best expertise to work on it. And we take care of all of the hassle that comes  with the work like contracts, invoices, compensation decisions, and payments of  experts.</p>\r\n  <h2>Changing your request  after it has been posted.</h2>\r\n  <p>Once your question has been posted, you can make  changes like extending the scope, adding tasks, extending the deadline if you  are not satisfied with the answers received, or increasing the budget. Our  Knowledge Manager will work with you throughout the whole process as required.</p>\r\n  <h2>Communicating with 10EQS  experts.</h2>\r\n  <p>For most fact finding knowledge engagements communication with  experts will not be necessary. Also any issues that need clarification during a  knowledge engagement we will clarify for you and in consultation with you. For  our more complex advisory type knowledge engagements direct communication  (typically by phone) with experts will be a possibility and can be arranged by  us on request.</p>\r\n  <h2>Receiving the results of  the work.</h2>\r\n  <p>Once all tasks of your question have been answered in the system,  our Knowledge Manager will compile the results and transmit them to you.  Depending on the engagement, the output can come in different formats. Results  of numerical fact-finding engagements will typically be transmitted in a  spreadsheet format; for advisory engagements, the format can be a combination  of text files and presentations.</p>\r\n  <h2>Paying experts for their  work.</h2>\r\n  <p>We will take care of paying the experts that have worked on the tasks  belonging to your question, in line with the budget that we have agreed with  you beforehand. You will receive from us an invoice that clearly specifies  which tasks have been solved and which ones not, and which of the experts that  have worked on your question should be paid how much. </p>\r\n  <h2>Receiving invoices from  experts.</h2>\r\n  <p>If needed, we will also generate automatically invoices to you  from all experts that receive compensation to ensure that you get complete  documentation for the work you contracted. There is no work for you to be done.</p>\r\n  <h2>Providing feedback to  10EQS and to experts.</h2>\r\n  <p>We encourage you to give us feedback as we want to  improve our service continuously and we need your input for it. You can also  give feedback to individual experts that have worked on advisory tasks of your  engagement. At this moment, this feedback should be channeled through the  Knowledge Manager; in the future, we will have a dedicated facility for this.</p>\r\n    <p>From our side, we will track  the actual activity of experts working on our platform and thus will have a  clear picture of which expert is most suited to work on your engagement.</p>\r\n  <h2>Contractual  relationships.</h2>\r\n  <p>When using 10EQS Knowledge Exchange, you are entering into a  platform usage contract with us, for which we will charge a usage fee. When  enquiring about posting an engagement, we will let you know what the current  fee is. Once your engagement is posted, you will enter into an automated  Knowledge Services Contract with those experts that are actually working on  your engagement and that are providing solutions. All contractual arrangements  are clearly spelled out in our Terms of Service. If you have any questions  about the contractual setup, please contact us under <a href=\"mailto:clients@10EQS.com\">clients@10EQS.com</a>.</p>\r\n                      <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n                      <p>Using 10EQS Knowledge  Exchange is an easy and straightforward process: you tell us which specific  question you would like to have answered and what you are willing to pay for it  and we will do the rest. You don’t have to worry about finding the right people,  contracting and paying them – this is all done by us. Here you find the details  of how it works.</p>','',1265279055,2),(6,6,1,'Contact us','\r\n&nbsp;\r\n                      <p>To find out more about how  10EQS Knowledge Exchange can benefit your business, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:clients@10EQS.com\">clients@10EQS.com</a>.</p>\r\n                       <p>You can find clear  explanations on how we work in the help file of our platform. Also the Terms of  Service are a good source of information on how we work. In addition, we  encourage you to contact us with any questions or comments. You can write us an  email under <a href=\"mailto:clients@10EQS.com\">clients@10EQS.com</a>.</p>\r\n                      <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n&nbsp;\r\n                      <p>To find out more about how  10EQS Knowledge Exchange can benefit your business, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:clients@10EQS.com\">clients@10EQS.com</a>.</p>\r\n                       <p>You can find clear  explanations on how we work in the help file of our platform. Also the Terms of  Service are a good source of information on how we work. In addition, we  encourage you to contact us with any questions or comments. You can write us an  email under <a href=\"mailto:clients@10EQS.com\">clients@10EQS.com</a>.</p>','',1265279167,2),(7,7,1,'Why 10EQS','                    \r\n                    <p>10EQS allows you to leverage  your expertise quickly and easily by working together with others on critical  issues for top clients around the world. When joining, you become part of an  exciting global community of professionals with whom you work, grow, and are  compensated for your contribution to solving important business problems. With  10EQS, helping top companies solve critical issues does not require privileged  client access or the relationships of a large organization; it is about being  recognized and rewarded for how you perform.</p>\r\n                    <h2>Join  now</h2>\r\n                    <p>We just started operations  and have posted the first client tasks on the platform. We will continuously  add new tasks as we are developing our client network. Some of these tasks  require specialist knowledge in an industry or function; many others can be  solved without specialist knowledge. We welcome anyone with expertise and the  desire to succeed to try us out.</p>\r\n                      <p>It takes only a few moments  to join our platform through a very simple registration process. Please use this <a href=\"https://app.10eqs.com/10eqs/register.html\" target=\"_blank\">link for registration</a>.  Once you have established your account in the system, you can immediately start  working. Use the filters supplied on the site to find the most suitable tasks  for you. With a few hours (and sometimes only minutes) of work you can earn  attractive compensation.</p>\r\n                    <h2>Why  working with us</h2>\r\n                    <p>Working in 10EQS Knowledge  Exchange is a challenging, fun, and convenient way to engage in interesting  client work, shape a new, innovative way to deliver knowledge to clients, and  monetize your expertise. You determine when you would like to work, how much  you would like to work, and what types of work you would like to do. You will  have the chance to meet other people online, collaborating and competing with  them. Through continuously upgrading your skills, you will get to ever more  complicated client projects. You can make a real career working with 10EQS  clients, and you can even build your own knowledge business on our platform.  Work with us – you will gain unique and global access to clients and you will  become part of a global network of exciting professionals.</p>\r\n                        <h2>Having global access to  clients.</h2>\r\n                        <p>We are out to crack the traditional client monopolies of closed  organizations in consulting, research and knowledge management. We believe that  there are lots of people around the globe that have much to contribute, and  that’s why we are offering you access to any clients and tasks where your  expertise can be brought to bear. </p>\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                      <li>Gain exposure to 10EQS clients around the world  and thus get a breadth of client access that would be difficult to obtain  otherwise</li>\r\n                      <li>Work on challenging projects in different  industries and functions, posted by sophisticated companies from around the  world</li>\r\n                      <li>Boost your revenue opportunities through working  on tasks that exactly match your expertise and specialization – tasks that  10EQS Knowledge Exchange will find for you</li>\r\n                      <li>Receive continuous support through a number of  tools, supporting documentation, feedback and direct coaching when working on  client projects</li>\r\n                    </ul><div class=\"padt5\"></div>\r\n                    <h2>Being part of a global  network.</h2>\r\n                    <p>10EQS is not just about working on client tasks; it is about  joining an exciting global community of like-minded professionals who are  similarly motivated to do excellent work. Almost all tasks require the  collaboration of many people; you work together and compete at the same time.  Through competitive collaboration you can learn from others and earn their  recognition. You will be able to team up with experts from anywhere in the world  and build your own professional community. Being an excellent performer will  automatically put you in touch with other excellent performers, and together  you will get access to top clients and the most exciting issues. </p>\r\n\r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','                    \r\n                    <p>10EQS allows you to leverage  your expertise quickly and easily by working together with others on critical  issues for top clients around the world. When joining, you become part of an  exciting global community of professionals with whom you work, grow, and are  compensated for your contribution to solving important business problems. With  10EQS, helping top companies solve critical issues does not require privileged  client access or the relationships of a large organization; it is about being  recognized and rewarded for how you perform.</p>','',1265279657,2),(8,8,1,'Our experts','                                       \r\n                    <p>10EQS experts are a select  group. Independent by design, they have chosen to pursue careers that give them  control over their professional lives, and flexibility to pursue their  passions. And given the wide range of client issues to be solved by them, our experts  span a wide range of qualifications.</p>\r\n                     <p>We are looking for  professionals that enjoy to work independently, prefer fast-paced challenges on  a continuous basis, want to make rapid progress in their careers, and like  collaborate with and compete against a global peer group. If you are  specialized in some area, and you want to take advantage of working  independently, you are the right person to register as an expert and build a  career on our platform. </p>\r\n\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                      <li>Develop and promote your expert status through  doing good client work, building your professional profile and rating and  getting to a more advanced skill category, becoming one of the most sought  after experts for more complex and rewarding tasks</li>\r\n                      <li>Distinguish yourself as a top performer in the  upper echelon of the 10EQS expert network and become eligible to participate in  ongoing, in-depth consulting projects</li>\r\n                      <li>Take additional responsibilities such as  developing other experts and becoming responsible for managing knowledge  engagements</li>\r\n                      <li>When having reached the status of an industry or  functional specialist, post a customized 10EQS Expert badge on your personal or  company Web site or blog</li>\r\n                      <li>Interact directly with other 10EQS experts for  peer-to-peer consulting. Then forge new relationships with your peers in 10EQS  Knowledge Exchange, working together with them on exciting client projects and  building relationships around the world</li>\r\n                      <li>Become an entrepreneur in 10EQS Knowledge  Exchange, forming your own, international knowledge business and offer your  expertise directly on our site </li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                      \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','                                       \r\n                    <p>10EQS experts are a select  group. Independent by design, they have chosen to pursue careers that give them  control over their professional lives, and flexibility to pursue their  passions. And given the wide range of client issues to be solved by them, our experts  span a wide range of qualifications.</p>','',1265279740,2),(9,9,1,'How to work with us','<p>At 10EQS, we know that our  strongest asset is you. We pride ourselves in offering interesting  possibilities to earn a living and become part of an exciting network to anyone  that wants to be a successful professional. If you are a professional with a  strong desire to succeed, we would love to hear from you. Here is how experts  work with us and with clients using 10EQS Knowledge Exchange.</p>\r\n<h2>Registering to become an  expert.</h2>\r\n<p>The first step is to set up an account with us. Setting up  an account is a simple straightforward process involving only a few steps such  as specifying your email, selecting a user ID and a password. Here is the <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://app.10eqs.com/10eqs/register.html\">link  to our registration page</a>. Once you have registered, you can  start to work immediately; no additional information is needed for that. Over  time, you can update your profile with additional information and change  several personal settings.</p>\r\n<h2>Determining your level of  expertise.</h2>\r\n<p>During registration, we will ask you to provide us with a  summary rating of your level of expertise. This will help us finding the right  tasks for you and thus will facilitate your being successful on the platform.  10EQS offers four different professional skill levels to its experts:  students/junior professionals, analysts, Industry/functional specialists, and  gurus. Please choose the appropriate one amount the first three for your  initial summary rating.</p>\r\n<p>The rating that you give  yourself during registration is to provide the right starting point for your  career in 10EQS; over time, you determine yourself through your work on 10EQS  Knowledge Exchange where you are, what tasks to work on and how you want to  develop.</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n    <li>As a student/junior professional, you have  access to a large variety of client tasks that require little or no experience  in an industry or function but do require good analytical skills and a strong  desire to be successful. You will compete and collaborate with your peers, and  you will get to know experts working with you on the same tasks and helping you  to develop.</li>\r\n    <li>Analysts have already a high level of expertise  in a given field, be it an industry or a function, typically in combination  with a geographic focus, and they have accumulated professional analytical  skills over a number of years in research jobs. As an analyst, you have access  to all tasks of students/junior professionals, and you can also solve tasks for  which specific experience is required.</li>\r\n    <li>Industry/functional specialists are true  specialists in an industry or function, accumulated over a number of years of  experience in companies and professional consulting firms. Experts will be  invited to work on advisory tasks, in addition to the tasks open to  students/junior professionals and analysts. Industry/functional specialists  will also collaborate on complex advisory engagements may have direct client  contact as needed.</li>\r\n    <li>Gurus are outstanding professionals in their  field of specialization, and they have made their mark over many years in the  respective industry or function. Gurus will often directly work with clients,  and they have a key role in the quality control of client engagements, the  development of other experts and the further evolution of the 10EQS system.</li>\r\n    <li>We at 10EQS want all of our experts to be  successful. We have various special development programs in place, helping you  to go through the different levels, continuously upgrade your skills and  eventually have the chance to become a guru in our system. To support you in  your development and to make sure that you get access to the tasks that you can  solve successfully, we will show you continuously where you stand and which  areas you should develop.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<div class=\"padt5\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Finding the right tasks.</h2>\r\n<p>The  most important key to being successful in 10EQS Knowledge Exchange is working  on those tasks whose specialization requirements exactly match your expertise.  With a few mouse clicks, you can find the tasks that you believe are the best  for you to work on. In addition, depending on your activity in the system,  10EQS will find those tasks that are most suitable for you and it will alert  you when something of interest is coming up.</p>\r\n<h2>Working on the platform.</h2>\r\n<p>Solving  tasks in 10EQS Knowledge Exchange is easy: each of the tasks has a clear  description, and a task solver box will show you what to do. Thus solving a  task and earning compensation is often a matter of minutes, giving you  attractive per diem rates when you add it all up. Each task is a unique little  project of its own, with its own deadline and budget and thus a clear  indication of what you can earn. We will group tasks that have similar  difficulty and are likely solved through the same methods to make it easier for  you to leverage your expertise and earn money.</p>\r\n<h2>Receiving compensation.</h2>\r\n<p>Once  you have solved a task successfully, we will take care of all the rest, making  sure that you will get your compensation quickly and without hassle. We will  invoice the client for whom you have worked on your behalf, collect the money  for you and transmit it to your PayPal account. We do require, at this moment,  that you have a PayPal account as this is the only way we can transmit  compensation to you in an easy and cost effective manner. We will not charge  you any fees for working on the site; all fees will be paid for by the client.  The amount of money that you see in the task description is the amount that you  can earn when providing a correct solution.</p>\r\n<p><a title=\"PayPal\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://www.paypal.com\"><img height=\"20\" border=\"none\" align=\"top\" width=\"42\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/paypal_img_icon.png\"></a></p>\r\n<h2>Viewing your current  performance ranking.</h2>\r\n<p>10EQS will keep a record of the tasks that you solved  successfully. Based on your activity, 10EQS will compute a ranking of your  performance. With this ranking 10EQS will be able to suggest to you those tasks  for which you have the right specialization. The higher the rank, the more  interesting tasks you will have access to and are notified of. You can view  your current performance ranking on the dashboard once you have logged into the  system.</p>\r\n<p>At 10EQS, we believe that our strength is our  people and they make the real difference. No organisation can fail with a group  of independent, motivated, energized and satisfied people working hard to  achieve their individual goals. As an organisation, the most important task for  us is to help our people become the best they can be and reach the absolute  peak of their potential. Each person is encouraged to take a personal  responsibility, and develop actively expertise and capabilities. We invite you  to register at 10EQS Knowledge Exchange and assure you that we will do our best  to make this a positive and rewarding experience!</p>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>','<p>At 10EQS, we know that our  strongest asset is you. We pride ourselves in offering interesting  possibilities to earn a living and become part of an exciting network to anyone  that wants to be a successful professional. If you are a professional with a  strong desire to succeed, we would love to hear from you. Here is how experts  work with us and with clients using 10EQS Knowledge Exchange.</p>','',1265803468,2),(10,10,1,'Contact us','                                                     \r\n                    <p>To participate in our  network and become an expert, please <a href=\"https://app.10eqs.com/10eqs/register.html\" target=\"_blank\">register here</a>.  If you would like more information about us, please send an email to <a href=\"mailto:experts@10EQS.com\">experts@10EQS.com</a>.</p>\r\n                    \r\n                    <p>Use your knowledge and  expertise to help top companies solve important business problems. Join us to  shape the future of this new workplace for experts and problem solvers!</p>\r\n                    \r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','                                                     \r\n                    <p>To participate in our  network and become an expert, please <a href=\"https://app.10eqs.com/10eqs/register.html\" target=\"_blank\">register here</a>.  If you would like more information about us, please send an email to <a href=\"mailto:experts@10EQS.com\">experts@10EQS.com</a>.</p>\r\n                    \r\n                    <p>Use your knowledge and  expertise to help top companies solve important business problems. Join us to  shape the future of this new workplace for experts and problem solvers!</p>','',1265279926,2),(11,11,1,'Overview','\r\n                    <div>\r\n                    <p>10EQS Knowledge Exchange is  a Swiss based online knowledge platform connecting clients with global top  talent in a structured, online environment. 10EQS enables clients to access  targeted, to the point knowledge fast and affordable, and it enables experts to  leverage their skills through working with clients around the world.</p>\r\n                      <p>10EQS clients include  professional services firms, leading industrial companies and government institutions.  10EQS experts span a wide range of industry, functional and/or consulting  experience, and they include industry and functional specialists, researchers,  analysts and qualified students. Our experts appreciate the ability offered by  10EQS to enhance their industry knowledge and monetize their skills on a  flexible basis. 10EQS operates globally across most industries. 10EQS adheres  to strict ethical values and compliance rules. </p>\r\n                      \r\n                      \r\n                    \r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n                    <div>\r\n                    <p>10EQS Knowledge Exchange is  a Swiss based online knowledge platform connecting clients with global top  talent in a structured, online environment. 10EQS enables clients to access  targeted, to the point knowledge fast and affordable, and it enables experts to  leverage their skills through working with clients around the world.</p>','',1265279990,2),(12,12,1,'Our Concept','\r\n\r\n                    <div>                   \r\n                    <p>10EQS Knowledge Exchange is  an online market that allows clients to buy, and experts to sell, knowledge in  a structured collaboration format – anywhere, anytime. We believe that the wisdom of many will always beat the insight of one, no  matter how specialized and experienced the one may be. As a new,  innovative market for expertise, 10EQS Knowledge Exchange addresses the needs  of both clients and professionals:</p>\r\n                    \r\n                    <ul>\r\n                      <li>Clients face rapidly growing needs for information  on an ever broader range of subjects, which the traditional paradigm of closed  organizations cannot meet. The knowledge economy of the future will require  opening up and working with everyone that has the expertise to contribute. </li>\r\n                      <li>Professionals face a similar dilemma: while  skills and capacity are available, direct access to clients is limited, and  finding the right tasks is often not possible. Only having access to all  clients in need of expertise will allow professionals to take advantage of their  skills and leverage their capabilities.</li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                    <div class=\" padt5\"></div>\r\n                    <p>Currently available  web-based offerings only partially respond to this need: functioning  collaboration sites (Wikipedia being the best example) have no commercial  model; many sites that have a commercial model operate like \"pay-by-number\"  phone books and offer connections but no solutions.</p>\r\n                      <p>10EQS Knowledge Exchange  addresses these shortcomings and offers an innovative answer to knowledge needs  of clients and the leverage requirements of professionals: our platform contains  a content-based structured communication interface between users and providers  of knowledge and a commercial framework for crowd-solving and mass  collaboration.</p>\r\n                    <p>The future \"wikinomics-style\" knowledge economy will  totally change the paradigms of working together. Traditional employment  relationships will continue to erode; long-term employment, which has already  been reduced through part-time and project-based work, will diminish further  and will be increasingly replaced by task-based cooperation. Corporations will  become smaller and bigger at the same time: staff on permanent contract will  decline, but corporations will work with anyone, anywhere, anytime that can  contribute. Professionals also stand to benefit from this development.  Privileged client relationships will diminish, and everyone will be able to  work on exactly the tasks that correspond to available expertise</p>\r\n                                        \r\n                    </div>                    \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n\r\n                    <div>                   \r\n                    <p>10EQS Knowledge Exchange is  an online market that allows clients to buy, and experts to sell, knowledge in  a structured collaboration format – anywhere, anytime. We believe that the wisdom of many will always beat the insight of one, no  matter how specialized and experienced the one may be. As a new,  innovative market for expertise, 10EQS Knowledge Exchange addresses the needs  of both clients and professionals:</p>','',1265280064,2),(13,13,1,'Our Mission','\r\n                    <div>\r\n                    <p>In \"technical\" language, our  mission is this: 10EQS aims at dramatically reducing transaction cost of  information through connecting clients with experienced professionals in a  structured content format for fact finding and problem solving, using  innovative crowd solving and mass collaboration techniques on a commercial  basis.</p>\r\n                      <p>But to put it into plain  English: we are out to crack traditional knowledge monopolies of closed  organizations. In effect we are \"democratizing\" access to knowledge, making it  affordable and available to a much larger audience. We believe that clients  should be able to work with everyone that can contribute – without paying large  institutional margins. And we believe that anyone who can contribute should  have access to matching client problems – without having to go through narrow  institutional bottlenecks.</p>\r\n                    \r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    \r\n                                       \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n                    <div>\r\n                    <p>In \"technical\" language, our  mission is this: 10EQS aims at dramatically reducing transaction cost of  information through connecting clients with experienced professionals in a  structured content format for fact finding and problem solving, using  innovative crowd solving and mass collaboration techniques on a commercial  basis.</p>','',1265280230,2),(14,14,1,'Our Value Proposition','\r\n                    \r\n                    <div>\r\n                    <p>We offer clients and experts  a distinct value proposition in using our site: collaborative problem solving  on demand on a global basis.</p>\r\n                      <h2>This is our value  proposition for clients:</h2>   \r\n                       <ul>\r\n                          <li>Unparalleled industry reach and depth: With  10EQS, clients get direct access to thousands of experts with deep expertise in  their fields.</li>\r\n                          <li>Mass collaboration – the wisdom of crowds:  Experts will work on a client problem in a collaborative mode; a task is  considered solved only once answers have passed several stringent quality tests. </li>\r\n                          <li>Speed: Since we will find the right experts with  the required knowledge for each client task, there is no time-consuming  “learning curve”. Also, since only timely solutions count, there is an  incentive for experts to solve client questions quickly.</li>\r\n                          <li>Costs: By accessing people with relevant  knowledge in an online environment we are able to keep our costs to a fraction  of what traditional knowledge providers charge. </li>\r\n                      </ul>\r\n                    <div class=\"padt5\"></div>                      \r\n                     <h2>This is our value proposition for experts: </h2>   \r\n                       <ul>\r\n                         <li>Monetize expertise: Over the years, professionals  accumulate significant experience within an industry or functional topic that  has a real value to others. 10EQS offers a well structured online environment  to monetize skills and increase utilization for any professional with specific  expertise and the will to succeed. </li>\r\n                         <li>Personal empowerment: 10EQS offers an efficient  way to access global clients on exciting projects. Individual consultants or  consulting firms can take advantage of this possibility and work with clients  that would be unreachable otherwise.</li>\r\n                         <li>Networking opportunities: 10EQS offers  attractive networking options for industry experts. Through working on the  platform in collaboration mode, experts can connect and exchange ideas with  other experts and grow their own skills and expertise.</li>\r\n                       </ul>\r\n                     \r\n                      \r\n                      \r\n                      \r\n                    \r\n                    </div>\r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n                    \r\n                    <div>\r\n                    <p>We offer clients and experts  a distinct value proposition in using our site: collaborative problem solving  on demand on a global basis.</p>','',1265280873,2),(15,15,1,'Our Values','\r\n\r\n                    <div>                   \r\n                    <p>Establishing a new knowledge  market means writing new rules that provide a fair balance between the  interests of all stakeholders. Our values reflect this objective. In  particular, we aspire to the following:</p>\r\n                    <ul>\r\n                      <li>We want to be better in our client work. We know  that clients have many possibilities to obtain knowledge. Companies may work  with many outside vendors, and they may hire large numbers of individual  outside contractors. We believe that with our setup we are the right complement  to a client organization: a large, global pool of experts, working on clearly  structured issues in collaboration mode will be in many cases the right way to  get external knowledge.</li>\r\n                      <li>We want our experts to be successful and to  develop. We will do our utmost to ensure that experts working on our site will  be successful. We will find the right work for you, help you in solving the  tasks that we identify, and make sure that you will get the compensation  associated with successful solutions easily. But working in 10EQS Knowledge  Exchange is not just about quick task solving; it is about continuous  professional growth through successful collaboration with others. Our systems,  in particular approach to evaluation, will make sure that experts get all the  support to develop.</li>\r\n                      <li>We want a fair balance between the interests of  clients and those of experts working for them. Clients want to have the best  insights in the shortest period of time at the lowest cost. Experts want to  work on the most challenging problems, leveraging and monetizing their expertise  to the highest degree possible. We believe that our  approach to a knowledge market with competitive collaboration provides a fair  balance. Clients determine the budget for solving their issues; experts decide  whether they will work on them. Competition is global and compensation for a  given task is the same anywhere. We make no difference between the  characteristics of anyone working on the site: 10EQS Knowledge Exchange is the  ultimate meritocracy, and anyone has the same chance to succeed.</li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n\r\n                    </div>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n\r\n                    <div>                   \r\n                    <p>Establishing a new knowledge  market means writing new rules that provide a fair balance between the  interests of all stakeholders. Our values reflect this objective. In  particular, we aspire to the following:</p>','',1265280941,2),(16,16,1,'Working with us','\r\n                    <p>Working with us is easy.  Clients can contact us by sending us an email to <a href=\"mailto:clients@10EQS.com\">clients@10EQS.com</a>. A Knowledge  Manager will get in touch with the respective client representative and discuss  with you your knowledge project. The Knowledge Manager will stay with you  throughout the knowledge project to make sure that your question gets answered  in the best possible way.</p>\r\n                     <p>Professionals that would  like to become experts can simply <a href=\"https://app.10eqs.com/10eqs/register.html\" target=\"_blank\">register through  this link</a>. As soon as you have registered, you can start to work on  the tasks that are currently posted.</p>\r\n\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                                        \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n                    <p>Working with us is easy.  Clients can contact us by sending us an email to <a href=\"mailto:clients@10EQS.com\">clients@10EQS.com</a>. A Knowledge  Manager will get in touch with the respective client representative and discuss  with you your knowledge project. The Knowledge Manager will stay with you  throughout the knowledge project to make sure that your question gets answered  in the best possible way.</p>','',1265281018,2),(17,17,1,'Compliance','<div class=\"main_content_area\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>We have strict compliance  rules to ensure that the interests of all parties concerned are properly  guarded. When working on our site, experts must agree to our Terms of Service,  which include clear restrictions on the information that experts can submit as  solutions to tasks. In particular, for a solution to be valid, a traceable  source must be submitted, and experts working for another institution must  receive the sign-off of their current employers that they can work on 10EQS  Knowledge Exchange.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>','<div class=\"main_content_area\">\r\n<div>\r\n<p>We have strict compliance  rules to ensure that the interests of all parties concerned are properly  guarded. When working on our site, experts must agree to our Terms of Service,  which include clear restrictions on the information that experts can submit as  solutions to tasks. In particular, for a solution to be valid, a traceable  source must be submitted, and experts working for another institution must  receive the sign-off of their current employers that they can work on 10EQS  Knowledge Exchange.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','',1265599754,2),(18,18,1,'Our Team','<p>10EQS is developing online solutions for information markets in management consulting. Our team brings together the cumulated expertise from different fields of practice: consulting and research, business and academics, communications and financial services, IT and online learning.</p>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Eberhard von L&ouml;hneysen</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"110\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/img_eberhardvonloehneysen1.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>Eberhard von L&ouml;hneysen, founder and chairman of the 10EQS group, has  built an extensive career in business consulting and corporate  management. After working at the World Bank with a focus on Latin  America for eight years, Eberhard spent more than two decades with  McKinsey &amp; Co. in different fields and countries. He was  responsible for the German financial institutions practice and managed  the McKinsey office in Berlin for several years; later he moved to  Moscow, where he was responsible for the Eastern European office  complex. He is intimately familiar with all aspects of consulting and  management processes. After leaving consulting, Eberhard most recently  worked as group CEO of a leading Russian consumer goods and financial  services conglomerate.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<h2>Henrik Poppe</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"110\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/Henrik_website.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>Henrik has a broad experience from industry, management consulting and investment banking. After serving in Merrill Lynch&rsquo;s M&amp;A team and in HSBC investment bank, Henrik spent more than eight years with McKinsey &amp; Co. based in Scandinavia and the Middle East. During his time in McKinsey, Henrik managed a broad range of projects within different industries and countries. His leadership responsibilities while at McKinsey &amp; Co. included responsibility for the Norwegian and Middle Eastern Corporate Finance practices. Henrik has been keynote speaker on several global conferences and been extensively quoted in well known publications as e.g. The Economist and Wallpaper. Henrik has thorough knowledge of all key aspects of consulting and management processes. After leaving McKinsey, Henrik served as group CFO and later group CEO of Russian Standard, one of Russia&rsquo;s leading consumer goods and financial services companies.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<h2>Lisa Harrison</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"110\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/Lisa_website.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>Lisa has over 20 years of combined card payments and broader retail  banking experience coupled with management consulting expertise, having  held senior roles at leading financial institutions both in Canada and  Europe. She is a known cards/payments expert with extensive background  in launching and managing card portfolios and driving performance  improvement strategies and programs. Most recently Lisa has been SVP,  European Regional Business Leader at MasterCard Advisors (9 years) with  earlier career roles at Citibank, American Express and CIBC.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<h2>Stefan Pap</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"112\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/Stefan_Pap3.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>Stefan has more than ten years of management consulting experience and  most recently worked as an independent consultant based in Switzerland.  His clients include some of the leading Swiss organizations. Stefan  started his career with Deloitte Consulting in Vienna and Zurich.  During four years at Deloitte, he supported financial services clients  across Europe on strategic and operational topics and took a key role  in building the Swiss CRM practice. Stefan later joined McKinsey &amp;  Company where he worked as an Engagement Manager in the Corporate  Finance practice and led several M&amp;A related projects for telecom,  manufacturing, and private equity clients. He holds an MBA from The  Kellogg School of Management at Northwestern University and a business  degree from Vienna University of Economics.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<h2>Sugath Warnakulasuriya</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"109\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/IMG_0345_v022.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>In recent years, Sugath has served Fortune 100 technology companies in  developing and executing growth, go-to-market, sales and product  portfolio management strategies. Previously, he was an Industry  Executive for EDS, managing the strategic direction of the company  within the high-tech industry, and at McKinsey &amp; Company, serving  enterprise software and financial services clients as a part of the  business technology practice. He also co-founded and was CTO of eLink  Commerce, a collaborative B2B logistics provider. Sugath&rsquo;s experience  includes developing and managing complex software and systems for GTE  Government Systems and SRA International among others. Sugath has a PhD  in Computer Engineering and a Masters in Computer Science from the  University of Southern California.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<h2>Felix C. Seyfarth</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"110\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/img_felixcseyfarth.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>Before joining 10EQS, Felix has been in charge of communicating a major  public sector restructuring project as Director of Marketing and  Communications at Leuphana University. His previous work experience  also includes Management Information Systems and Global Helpdesk of  Deutsche Bank AG, New York and the Public Information Department of the  United Nations Headquarters in New York. He has overseen, coordinated  and implemented various projects for process-driven, interactive and  educational web applications. Felix holds a degree in Political Science  from Free University Berlin, Germany and is preparing a dissertation at  the University of St. Gallen, Switzerland.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<h2>Andr&eacute;s von L&ouml;hneysen</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"110\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/img_andresvonloehneysen1.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>Andr&eacute;s\' practical experience stems from various internships in the  financial services industry, such as conducting due diligence for DLJ  Merchant Banking Partners London, UK, the private equity branch of  Credit Suisse, and modelling DCF valuations to assist in investment  decisions at the Warburg Value Fund for M. M. Warburg Bank in Z&uuml;rich,  Switzerland. Andr&eacute;s holds a degree in Economics from the University of  Freiburg, Germany. His diploma thesis focused on the use of intangible  assets as funding source and investment product, a project conducted in  cooperation with the McKinsey Risk Management Practice Frankfurt,  Germany.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<h2>Andrea Wuchner</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"110\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/img_andreawuchner2.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>Andrea&rsquo;s previous experience includes human resources, controlling and  account management, as well as sales and marketing gained from working  for various international companies in different commercial  environments. Andrea studied economics and psychology in Basel.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<h2>M&eacute;lanie Chopard</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"110\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/Melanie_website-copy.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>M&eacute;lanie previously worked as an intern in the Department of Public  Information at the United Nations Headquarters in New York, as well as  in the Permanent Mission of Switzerland to the UN in Geneva. She holds  a Masters in Public Communication from the University of Lugano,  Switzerland.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<h2>Manuel Ziegler</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"110\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/Manuel_website.jpg\" /></div>\r\n<div>Manuel\'s practical experience includes the areas of information economics, marketing and insurance, and most recently he has worked for a consulting company in the renewable energy sector. Manuel holds a degree of Economics from the University of Freiburg, Germany.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"padt10\">\r\n<h2>Ajten Dshabarowa</h2>\r\n<div class=\"content_in_image\"><img height=\"110\" width=\"92\" alt=\"\" src=\"/sites/all/themes/teneqs/images/Ajten_website.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<div>Ajten previously worked in the travel business where she managed commercial activities and was responsible for customer-service and back-office tasks.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>','<p>10EQS is developing online solutions for information markets in management consulting. Our team brings together the cumulated expertise from different fields of practice: consulting and research, business and academics, communications and financial services, IT and online learning.</p>','',1265797744,2),(19,19,1,'Contact us','\r\n\r\n                    <div>\r\n                    <p><strong>10EQS  Knowledge Exchange</strong><br>\r\n                      Via  Molinazzo 2<br>\r\n                      CH-6900  Lugano<br>\r\n                      Switzerland<br>\r\n                      Phone  +41 (91) 266-7000 <br>\r\n                      <a href=\"mailto:info@10EQS.com\">info@10EQS.com</a></p>\r\n                  \r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n\r\n                    <div>\r\n                    <p><strong>10EQS  Knowledge Exchange</strong><br>\r\n                      Via  Molinazzo 2<br>\r\n                      CH-6900  Lugano<br>\r\n                      Switzerland<br>\r\n                      Phone  +41 (91) 266-7000 <br>\r\n                      <a href=\"mailto:info@10EQS.com\">info@10EQS.com</a></p>\r\n                  \r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n                    <p>&nbsp;</p>','',1265281374,2),(20,20,1,'General Questions','\r\n                   \r\n                    <div>                  \r\n                    \r\n                    <h3>What is 10EQS Knowledge  Exchange?</h3>\r\n                    <p>10EQS Knowledge Exchange is  an online platform that offers knowledge services to solve client problems,  using crowd solving and mass collaboration techniques. 10EQS provides a  convenient way for clients to structure questions (simple fact needs or complex  problems) through an industry-specific \"content language\". 10EQS will then  disaggregate the client question into individual tasks and post it to a global  pool of specialized experts, who can solve them either independently (crowd  solving) or collaboratively (mass collaboration). </p>\r\n                    <h3>What is the basic idea of  10EQS Knowledge Exchange? </h3>\r\n                    <p>10EQS Knowledge Exchange  aspires to make knowledge accessible and affordable, cracking the current  monopolies of large, closed organizations. Access to and use of knowledge  should be universal. A client with a problem should have access to anyone with  the knowledge to crack it – anywhere, at any time. And anyone with knowledge  should have access to any client in need for it – anywhere, at any time. </p>\r\n                    <h3>What are your key methods  and concepts?</h3>\r\n                    <p>We have created a  proprietary industry model that allows clients to structure business issues in  a way easily understood by expert professionals. Client problems of varying  degrees of complexity will be broken up into small, self-contained tasks and  posted on our site. Based on their specialization, experts are selected for  those tasks and work on them in parallel; their solutions are re-assembled  submitted to the client. Our proprietary model allows finding and matching a  client issue to the most suited set of experts. We also have developed a  proprietary set of rules for competitive collaboration that combines the  dynamic pressure of competition with the creativity of collaboration.</p>\r\n                    <h3>How do you get so many  professionals working independently to produce a common result? </h3>\r\n                    <p>We harness the power of a  new mode of working: a large group of people combine their expertise and  knowledge base within our competitive collaboration rules to arrive at an  aggregated solution. Many studies as well as practical examples have shown that  the \"wisdom of crowds\" yields better results than individual experts or small  groups.</p>\r\n                    <h3>What is crowd solving?</h3>\r\n                    <p>Crowd solving refers to a  new mode of developing solutions to problems - a large group of people working  independently on a task, not knowing the approaches and solutions of others  working on the same task. Experience has shown that the collective problem  solving power of a crowd of independent experts often yields better results  than that of any individual expert or small group. This concept is often  referred to as \"wisdom of crowds\".</p>\r\n                    <h3>What is mass collaboration?</h3>\r\n                    <p>Mass collaboration means  that a large group of people work collaboratively on the same task, being able  to communicate with each other and exchange ideas to come to an aggregate  solution. The idea of mass collaboration takes the approach of crowd solving  but develops it one step further: it uses not only the power of crowds but also  the communication among the members of a crowd to come up with solutions that  are even better than those developed independently by members of a crowd.</p>\r\n                    <h3>What do clients gain from  working with 10EQS? </h3>\r\n                    <p>We offer clients access to a  large pool of expert knowledge and research skills for pressing business issues  and strategic management questions. With this pool of experts and our  proprietary methods, clients will be able to achieve substantial gains in  efficiency, quality and speed when resolving critical business issues. </p>\r\n                    <h3>What do experts gain from  working with 10EQS? </h3>\r\n                    <p>We offer experts the  possibility of working on important business issues for top companies from all  over the world as well as leveraging their expertise while working from  anywhere and at any time. They will work according to a structured set of rules  and receive compensation accordingly. They will form part of an exciting global  community of professionals and will have the opportunity to grow professionally  and be recognized and rewarded for their contribution.</p>\r\n                    <h3>Is 10EQS a form of  outsourcing?</h3>\r\n                    <p>10EQS offers a completely  new collaboration paradigm, replacing traditional forms of structured  employment through competitive collaboration. In contrast, outsourcing  continues with the traditional employment paradigm; it only splits out one  function of a company and puts it into another company to reduce management  load and costs. </p>\r\n                    <h3>What is the difference  between 10EQS Knowledge Exchange and other expert sites? </h3>\r\n                    <p>10EQS Knowledge Exchange  solves a client’s business problems through getting specialized experts to work  on structured knowledge engagements of clients. 10EQS is a true \"Wikinomics\"  site, using the principles of crowd solving and mass collaboration to solve  client problems. The client defines the question; the rest is up to us. <br>\r\n                      In contrast, some other  sites are like paid phone books: they just sell the individual phone number of  a person that may (or may not) have an answer to a client question. The client  gets the phone number, and then needs to do all the rest .</p>\r\n                    <h3>What does \"10EQS\" stand  for? </h3>\r\n                    <p>\"10EQS\" is our aspiration:  creating a business that is at least 10 times better than anything comparable  in efficiency (\"E\"), quality (\"Q\") and speed (\"S\"). </p>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n                   \r\n                    <div>                  \r\n                    \r\n                    <h3>What is 10EQS Knowledge  Exchange?</h3>\r','',1265281609,2),(21,21,1,'For clients','\r\n                   \r\n                    <div>\r\n                    <h3>Why should my organization  become a client of 10EQS Knowledge Exchange?</h3>\r\n                    <p>As 10EQS client, you gain  access to a worldwide pool of  knowledge and expertise competitively collaborating to deliver the best  solutions to your problems, while the service is offered at a fraction of the  usual cost and the usual time of a management consulting study done in the  classical way. </p>\r\n                    <h3>How do I use 10EQS?</h3>\r\n                    <p>The first step is to contact  us through sending an email to <a href=\"mailto:clients@10EQS.com\">clients@10EQS.com</a>. A 10EQS  Knowledge Manager will get in touch with you, help you to specify your problem,  and make a specific proposal on how to solve your question through using our  site. Given the tools available for structuring knowledge engagements, it will  typically take only a few days to translate the initial question into a  knowledge engagement that can be posted on our site.<br>\r\n                      Once your engagement has  been created, it will be disaggregated into many small tasks on which experts  will then work without requiring further intervention from you. You can decide  whether engagements will be posted for everybody or only for a restricted  audience. Once experts have provided the solutions to the individual tasks, the  Knowledge Manager will pull the results together and transmit them to you.</p>\r\n                    <h3>What is  the range of problems for which clients can use 10EQS Knowledge Exchange? </h3>\r\n                    <p>In principle, any business  problem is suitable to be posted on 10EQS Knowledge Exchange. We have a process  for straightforward fact-finding issues as well as one for qualitative advisory  problems. With the structure of our site and the tools that we are offering, we  aim at providing solutions to all business issues by leveraging global  knowledge of different experts. We are best at answering specific questions  that require external knowledge like market overviews, best practice  assessments and benchmarking studies, but we will continuously expand our  capabilities into more complex subjects.</p>\r\n                    <h3>How do I assign and track  the status of my engagement?</h3>\r\n                    <p>The assignment of tasks to  experts is done automatically by the system; it will find those experts that  have the highest likelihood of coming up with the right answer. At any given  moment, your Knowledge Manager will be available to tell you where your project  stands. In the future, we will have a direct interface for you so that you can  track your projects online.</p>\r\n                    <h3>Who are the experts on 10EQS? </h3>\r\n                    <p>The 10EQS expert base  consists of individuals or firms having specific industry/functional/topical  knowledge, analytical capabilities as well as the time to solve client  problems. 10EQS experts comprise a large variety of different segments,  including free-lance experts, part-time professionals, former executives,  researchers, and academics (including qualified students). What 10EQS experts  have in common is expertise in some area and willingness to bring it to bear on  client problems that are matching their skills. Most of the experts are  individuals; however, 10EQS is also open to consulting firms and other  knowledge organizations and encourages them to use the platform.</p>\r\n                    <h3>How do I know whether there  are any experts that can solve my engagement?</h3>\r\n                    <p>With a quickly growing  number of industry specialists, 10EQS\' expert community will offer a wide range  of skills and capabilities for each industry covered. Within the expert  community, there will be specialists for almost any question that a client can  ask in one industry. In addition, we are constantly recruiting new experts to  register and work on our site so chances are that we have the specialty for the  particular business issue at hand.</p>\r\n                    <h3>How does 10EQS ensure that  experts really have the required knowledge? </h3>\r\n                    <p>We rely primarily on what  people do on our site, because \"formal\" qualifications may often not  sufficiently represent the true expertise that a person has. As experts are  becoming active on the site, 10EQS will create a detailed performance track  record through a proprietary rating mechanism, and it will apply this  performance rating when searching for experts to solve a particular client problem.</p>\r\n                    <h3>Do I need to find the right experts for my engagement?</h3>\r\n                    <p>Through a proprietary  algorithm, 10EQS will find those experts in its knowledge community that are  most likely to have an accurate answer for your specific question. You can also  specify the type of specialization that you would like experts to have when  working on your question. </p>\r\n                    <h3>When are the tasks of an engagement  solved successfully on 10EQS?</h3>\r\n                    <p>The tasks of an engagement  are solved successfully if they have been completed according to our Task Completion  and Compensation Rules. These rules include a number of different quality  checks, which partially are being done automatically by the system and  partially manually. In many cases, we will require for a single task more than  one solution coming from different experts. </p>\r\n                    <h3>How  does 10EQS ensure the quality of engagement solutions?</h3>\r\n                    <p>10EQS has an elaborate  proprietary quality checking mechanism: each solution provided by an expert is  subject to several checks of validity and traceability. While we do not claim  to provide you with the one and only \"true\" answer to your question (because  often there are several answers possible), we offer you a sophisticated process  to find a solution that as good as can be. All clients will get a detailed  explanation of our quality assurance process. </p>\r\n                    <h3>How do I know that the  solutions I receive are not based on illegal insider information?</h3>\r\n                    <p>When registering, experts  will have to agree to our Terms of Service, stating that the expert will not  disclose any confidential information on the 10EQS Knowledge Exchange. Also, to  be valid a solution submitted to the platform needs to have a traceable source.</p>\r\n                    <h3>How do  I communicate with experts working on my engagements?</h3>\r\n                    <p>In many of the fact-finding  engagements, there is no need to communicate directly with them. All necessary  communication will be done through the system to give you maximum transparency  with the least amount of effort while fully protecting your confidentiality  from others, especially your competitors. In complex advisory engagements, you  have the option to communicate directly with experts if needed.</p>\r\n                    <h3>How do  I know how much work the expert actually did to come up with a solution?</h3>\r\n                    <p>In fact you won’t know. Our  system is not based on hourly rates or per diems, and the time required does  not matter. The only thing that counts is whether an expert has delivered a  good result or not. The quality of the result we are checking very carefully  according to our Task Completion and Compensation Rules, and only results that  meet all of our criteria will be accepted. In addition, we will often require  more than one result (from more than one expert) for a task to be completed.</p>\r\n                    <h3>How much does the solution to my  engagement cost?</h3>\r\n                    <p>As a client, you determine  yourself how much money you believe you should pay for the engagements that you  would like to post. In other words, you set the budget. We will give you  recommendations on what we believe an adequate budget is, but ultimately it is your  decision. Obviously, if the budget for an engagement is too low, not many  experts are likely to work on it and you may want to raise the budget to get a  better response.</p>\r\n                    <h3>How does 10EQS  protect intellectual property (IP)?</h3>\r\n                    <p>Every registered expert in  the 10EQS network has agreed to the Terms of Service, which include an  extensive set of rules protecting intellectual property of all stakeholders.  That contractual protection is passed to the client on any active 10EQS assignment  as long as work and payment are performed through 10EQS. </p>\r\n                   \r\n\r\n                    </div>\r\n                    \r\n                         \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n                   \r\n                    <div>\r\n                    <h3>Why should my organization  become a client of 10EQS Knowledge Exchange?</h3>\r\n                    <p>As 10EQS client, you gain  access to a worldwide pool of  knowledge and expertise competitively collaborating to deliver the best  solutions to your problems, while the service is offered at a fraction of the  usual cost and the usual time of a management consulting study done in the  classical way. </p>','',1265281683,2),(22,22,1,'For experts','\r\n                   \r\n                    <div>\r\n                                  <h3>Why should I work as an individual in 10EQS Knowledge  Exchange?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>As a 10EQS expert you can earn money for  solving client tasks, thus leveraging your skills and expertise, and you become  part of an exciting global community of other experts with whom you collaborate  and compete. 10EQS offers you a structured marketplace where you can gain  access to a large variety of renowned clients anywhere in the world, and 10EQS  matches the tasks that clients are posting with your specific field of  knowledge. </p>\r\n                                  <h3>How do I join 10EQS?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>Setting up an account is a  simple straightforward process involving only a few steps such as specifying  your email, selecting a user ID and a password. Here is the <a href=\"https://app.10eqs.com/10eqs/register.html\" target=\"_blank\">link  to our registration page</a>. Once you have registered, you can  start to work immediately; no additional information is needed for that. Over  time, you can update your profile with additional information and change  several personal settings. Registration is free for both clients and experts. </p>\r\n                                  <h3>Can my company provide  services on 10EQS?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>Of course, you can sign up  as the manager of your company to become a 10EQS affiliate. Then add  individuals from your company to your company roster and work on client  engagements. All rates and payments will be in your control as the manager. We  encourage knowledge based organizations, consulting firms and research  companies to become experts as an institution. Please contact us under <a href=\"mailto:experts@10EQS.com\">experts@10EQS.com</a> if you would like to join our expert network as a company.</p>\r\n                                  <h3>What kinds of clients are  on the 10EQS Knowledge Exchange?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>Most 10EQS clients will be  among the largest corporations in the world. Thus through 10EQS, you will get  access to a clientele that you may find difficult to get in any other way.</p>\r\n                                  <h3>How do I get to work on a  task?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>A couple of things we  recommend: First, when registering and creating your profile, complete the  self-assessment of your skills as accurately as possible. 10EQS provides a list  of industry-specific expertise that you may have as a potential expert and that  clients may want to see of experts working on their tasks. If you fill it out,  the system will then have a basis to suggest tasks that are matching your  profile. Being accurate is critical; over-evaluating your expertise in too many  fields will be interpreted by the system as a low degree of specialization and  may work against you. Also, if you claim a high degree of specialization, the  system then will expect you to be a successful expert and it will quickly  discover any discrepancy through tracking your actual activity.</p>\r\n                                  <h3>How long does it take to be able to work on a task?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>This depends entirely on  you. Many if not most tasks are open to all experts and stay open until a  sufficient number of solutions has been submitted and accepted according to our  Task Completion and Compensation Rules. Thus, if you know your subject, are  fast enough, and come up with good results that are accepted by the system, you  can earn very attractive per diem rates, often above what you may currently  earn.</p>\r\n                                  <h3>How  do I deliver the solutions?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>You type your solutions for  tasks online directly in the respective task-solving interface. All other tests  and checks will then be done by the system.</p>\r\n                                  <h3>How do I communicate with  my client?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>This depends on the project.  In many fact-finding engagements there is no need for direct communication with  the client. In the more complex advisory engagements, client communication may  be part of the problem solving process, and 10EQS provides the communication  infrastructure in that situation through the crowd solving and collaboration  tools of the site.</p>\r\n                                  <h3>How do feedback and  evaluation work?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>10EQS has an elaborate  evaluation system called “ICPS”. The letters stand for Intensity, Complexity, Performance,  and Specialization. Intensity measures the total amount of your activity in the  system; complexity, the average size of the tasks you have worked on;  performance, how many of the solutions that you submitted were actually  accepted; and specialization tracks exactly for which types of tasks you have  worked. Thus, your overall standing depends on how much you are using the  system, how complex the tasks are and how often your solutions are being  accepted for any given specialization that you have worked on.</p>\r\n                                  <h3>How can I improve my  profile?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>The best way to get a better  profile is by working successfully on as many tasks as possible. The system is  recording all what you do, and every successful task will add to the quality of  your profile, leading to more work being offered and to a higher compensation. </p>\r\n                                  <h3>Can I get full time work?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>Sure, lots of people  eventually will. Build up your 10EQS reputation and satisfy clients through  submitting accepted answers and you may soon find yourself busy all the time. </p>\r\n                                  <h3>What is 10EQS’ compensation policy?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>If you are submitting a  solution to a task, and your solution gets accepted, clients will be charged  automatically and you will be paid automatically. The system has been set up in  such a way that any disputes about quality of work and obligations to pay will  be minimized.</p>\r\n                                  <h3>What  is the pay rate for a professional like me?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>There is no particular pay  rate for any individual because your income will entirely depend on the type  and number of tasks you are completing successfully. Of course, you can  implicitly achieve or increase a certain pay rate if you focus on more complex  tasks that require a higher level of specialization and have a higher budget.</p>\r\n                                  <h3>How much money can I make?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>That\'s all up to you.  Earning a good reputation and high feedback scores in the network can help you  achieve dramatic earnings growth and 10EQS can become the primary source of  your personal income – or company revenue. </p>\r\n                                  <h3>How  can I receive my payments?</h3>\r\n                                  <p>We will make it easy for you  to receive your compensation, no matter where you are. At this moment, the  primary source of payment will be through a PayPal account. In the future, we  may add internationally accepted prepaid cards as an additional payment option  for you.</p>\r\n                                  <h3>What about taxes?</h3>\r\n                      <p>As a client, you do not need  to pay any additional taxes if you\'re purchasing services through 10EQS.  Depending on which experts are working on your tasks and become eligible for  compensation, you will need to pay exactly the same amount of VAT or sales tax  that you would pay if you were to contract the experts directly.</p>\r\n                                    <p>European experts need to  specify during the registration process whether they are subject to VAT or not.  U.S.-based experts needing to fill out a W-9 form and 1099s will get them  provided at the end of the year. All experts are responsible for reporting  their earnings to the appropriate tax authorities. </p>\r\n  <h3>How do I know whether I  am permitted to work on a particular task?</h3>\r\n  <p>If you are in doubt, do not work on it. You may be subject to one or more  confidentiality agreements that prevent you from providing certain information.  Also, certain kinds of information are likely confidential in nature and for  that reason must not be disclosed to our clients, including but not limited to  information about earnings projections and other forecasts, corporate  strategies, unpublished clinical trial data, regulatory approval for a drug,  new product developments and inventions, awards of large contracts, significant  litigation, proposed mergers or acquisitions or any other significant but  undisclosed negative or positive news relevant to a particular industry or  company. </p>\r\n  <h3>What are the Terms of  Service?</h3>\r\n  <p>The Terms of Service is a binding contract between 10EQS and its experts.  It is designed to protect experts, clients and 10EQS. Among other things, it  requires 10EQS experts to honor their obligations to employers and other third  parties, and it requires experts to follow 10EQS’additional rules. For example,  10EQS prohibits experts from consulting about their own companies. The Terms of  Service also require experts to keep any information they learn about clients  and about their projects strictly confidential.</p>\r\n  <h3>Who  is responsible for determining my eligibility to join 10EQS Knowledge Exchange  and to work on tasks posted in it?</h3>\r\n  <p>You are. 10EQS does not make that determination for you. Prior to joining  the 10EQS you should review employment agreements, employee manuals, codes of  conduct, consulting agreements and other similar policies and agreements (in  each case as applicable) and check with employers or other third parties as  necessary. Once you have joined 10EQS, it is your responsibility to decline to  work on tasks that are inappropriate for you and to decline to discuss topics  that present a conflict for you.</p>\r\n  <h3>Do some companies have  policies about their employees doing outside consulting?</h3>\r\n                                    <p>Yes. Some companies have policies concerning participation in outside  consulting activities by their employees, and you should confirm with your  employer whether you are subject to a policy. You must comply with any such  restrictions. </p>\r\n  <h3>Does 10EQS keep my  information confidential? </h3>\r\n                                   <p>You should not join 10EQS Knowledge Exchange if you would not want your  participation to be known to your employer or to other third parties to whom  you owe obligations. In the interest of transparency, 10EQS reserves the right  to share information about you with your current employer and to anyone else  whose consent may be relevant to your participation in 10EQS Knowledge Exchange  or in a particular engagement. 10EQS will not sell or license your information  to a third party for marketing purposes.</p>\r\n  <h3>Can I tell people about  the tasks on which I have worked?</h3>\r\n                      <p>No. 10EQS experts are required to keep all projects confidential, including the  existence of the project, the identity of the client and the subject matter  discussed. </p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n                    \r\n                         \r\n                    \r\n                    \r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n                   \r\n                    <div>\r\n                                  <h3>Why should I work as an individual in 10EQS Knowledge  Exchange?</h3>\r','',1265281862,2),(23,23,1,'Contact','\r\n                    <p>If you would like to find out more about using 10EQS to solve your business problems, please send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:clients@10eqs.com\">clients@10eqs.com</a></p>\r\n                    \r\n<p>If you would like to find out more about becoming an expert, please send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:experts@10eqs.com\">experts@10eqs.com</a></p>\r\n\r\n                    <p>\r\n                    <strong>10EQS Knowledge Exchange</strong><br>\r\n                    Via Molinazzo 2<br>\r\n                    CH-6900 Lugano<br>\r\n                    Switzerland<br>\r\n                    Phone +41 (91) 266-7000<br>\r\n                    <a href=\"mailto:info@10EQS.com\">info@10EQS.com</a> </p>\r\n\r\n                    <div class=\"clear\"></div>\r\n                    ','\r\n                    <p>If you would like to find out more about using 10EQS to solve your business problems, please send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:clients@10eqs.com\">clients@10eqs.com</a></p>\r\n                    \r\n<p>If you would like to find out more about becoming an expert, please send us an email to <a href=\"mailto:experts@10eqs.com\">experts@10eqs.com</a></p>','',1265282034,2),(24,24,1,'What to expect from the 10EQS platform in 2010','<div class=\"main_content_area\">\r\n<div id=\"full_news\">\r\n<p>Dear 10EQS Experts,</p>\r\n<p>On behalf of the whole 10EQS team, I wish you a happy and prosperous 2010.</p>\r\n<p>In building on our success from last year, we are continuing to enhance our service offering to provide a distinctive, high-value experience for both our clients and experts. In particular, we will be introducing a number of new and exciting features on the 10EQS platform in the coming year.</p>\r\n<p>In addition to the opportunity to solve new types of client problems ranging from performing basic research to providing expert advice, we will provide a number of convenience features to better enable you to find, work on, and manage client engagements and tasks according to your skills and preferences. You will also gain access to on-line learning, support and guidance to become highly effective and successful on the 10EQS platform. You will be able to build and manage your on-line profile, plan and track your professional development, connect with others to share advice, mentor and be mentored, be recognized by others for your performance, and continually enhance your ability to earn by serving top clients on the 10EQS platform.</p>\r\n<p>As always, your input, feedback and suggestions are highly appreciated. Feel free to contact us at any time, open discussions in the group or write us while working in the system.</p>\r\n<p>We thank you for your support in 2009, and we are looking forward to an exciting 2010!</p>\r\n<p>Best Regards,</p>\r\n<strong>Sugath Warnakulasuriya<br />\r\nChief Technology Officer</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"main_title\">\r\n<div class=\"float_l title_bdrbtm\"><span>Season update from 10EQS</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"main_content_area\">\r\n<div id=\"full_news\">\r\n<p>Dear 10EQS community,</p>\r\n<p>At 10EQS we are excited about the future and what it&nbsp;holds for our  company. We believe that we are at the forefront of the web 3.0 transformation  &ndash; enabling people to collaborate and solve complex business issues in a truly  seamless environment. We have now tried out our model on a set of challenging  client engagements with encouraging results. The knowledge revolution begins now.</p>\r\n<p>A key reason for why we are confident about our future is because of our  experts. The experts which &ldquo;drive&rdquo; the 10EQS knowledge platform are the reason  for our progress to date and they will be the reason for our success in the  future. We believe 10EQS to be an exceptional company - a company of people  proud of the work they do, the solutions they provide and the knowledge  revolution they are part of. 10EQS is an organization defined by the character  and integrity of its people.</p>\r\n<p>As we work to serve our clients, to build strong relationships and  deliver innovative and creative solutions to their business challenges, we rely  on our core principles to guide our decisions and actions, ensuring everything  we do are beneficial to the client, or experts and our colleagues.</p>\r\n<p>I speak for all of the exceptional experts and employees at 10EQS when I say we  are totally committed to providing cheap, distinct, targeted knowledge to our  clients. We believe our responsibility is not only to ensure that we continue  to live up to the standards we have set, but also to advance our service to our  clients to even higher levels.</p>\r\n<p>As 10EQS&rsquo;s business grows, so does our opportunity to have a greater  impact on the world around us. Our recent series of meetings in Silicon Valley  where we met the globally leading players within crowd solving, professional  networking as well as venture capitalists only strengthened our belief in the  soundness of our mission and the uniqueness and the inherent potential that it  embodies.</p>\r\n<p>Thank you for your interest in 10EQS and for visiting our website. I  hope you find it informative. However, if you really want to get to know us and  what we can do to help you address your business challenges then please contact  us. We welcome the opportunity to connect with you and to contribute to your  success.</p>\r\n<p>Your sincerely,</p>\r\n<strong>Henrik  Poppe<br />\r\nChief  Executive Officer</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"clear\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>','<div class=\"main_content_area\">\r\n<div id=\"full_news\">\r\n<p>Dear 10EQS Experts,</p>\r\n<p>On behalf of the whole 10EQS team, I wish you a happy and prosperous 2010.</p>\r\n<p>In building on our success from last year, we are continuing to enhance our service offering to provide a distinctive, high-value experience for both our clients and experts. In particular, we will be introducing a number of new and exciting features on the 10EQS platform in the coming year.</p>','',1265802774,2),(25,25,1,'Template 1 Sample','','','',1265948463,2);
